{"tid":337853,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[nursing巴絲入] 讀返bio補底一問","createTime":"2017-07-27T16:14:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T03:53:32.000Z","uid":97908,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"67cb5c91da9bd092d835f28ae17f4dcfe031fdca","tid":337853,"uid":97908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T16:14:48.000Z","msg":"小弟黎緊9月讀asso 將來想入返u讀nursing<br />\n但小弟高中冇修bio 驚自己將來會爛grade<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  所以想讀返啲bio打返少少底先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想請教下各位讀nursing嘅巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果想預習定嘅話要讀啲咩先？或者有啲咩bio野係讀nursing基本要識嘅？有咩係遲啲會學/會用/會考？<br />\n等小弟可以讀住先 打返個底 因為小弟好想入返u<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感激不盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9fb0d2b3b60c12c4f62790d76049a131565cc97","tid":337853,"uid":75488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T16:33:07.000Z","msg":"anatomy同physiology"},{"pid":"3a5025703653428544502ed27e3140a0cb5a8141","tid":337853,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T16:37:03.000Z","msg":"你不如搵定師兄師姐借asso notes比你好過啦 然後針對性溫習"},{"pid":"e8ee840ec7dd8a79987dcd8728f41084062b5ece","tid":337853,"uid":90702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T16:57:36.000Z","msg":"hkcc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<br />\n不過基本上asso有關health個啲野都係會要你讀human biology<br />\nHKU space同CUSCS就唔清楚<br />\nhkcc hu bio有分I同II<br />\nbio I讀cell structure+osmosis+diffusion+ integumentary system+muscle+blood+bone+lymphatic system<br />\n應該係 除非唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01d1a579086923a1d5f57bc11752b71023df5d0e","tid":337853,"uid":97908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T17:12:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你不如搵定師兄師姐借asso notes比你好過啦 然後針對性溫習</blockquote><br />\n我都有諗過不過我冇識嘅師兄師姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝巴打先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我再睇睇會唔會有朋友識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5165d3094692a328c247a4b30ebe07ee125f8a87","tid":337853,"uid":92468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T17:15:52.000Z","msg":"Respiratory system<br />\nDigestive system<br />\nReproductive system<br />\nLymphatic system <br />\nNervous system <br />\n呢啲基本啦"},{"pid":"06359ad8a200763dd1ccddb1d0f06cbe47397a16","tid":337853,"uid":97908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T17:16:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>hkcc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<br />\n不過基本上asso有關health個啲野都係會要你讀human biology<br />\nHKU space同CUSCS就唔清楚<br />\nhkcc hu bio有分I同II<br />\nbio I讀cell structure+osmosis+diffusion+ integumentary system+muscle+blood+bone+lymphatic system<br />\n應該係 除非唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSpace呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過都多謝絲打咁有心覆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我會睇下呢方面既野 終於搵到啲方向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"619480b563704ded9c65d4818c7fc8e38ea97e47","tid":337853,"uid":97908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T17:25:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Respiratory system<br />\nDigestive system<br />\nReproductive system<br />\nLymphatic system <br />\nNervous system <br />\n呢啲基本啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實需唔需要好詳細咁熟讀哂每個system入面嘅部位？例如每一樣野既功能同特點？<br />\nthx絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1344c53e172ae953f2d4792abe547eb9cf2f591","tid":337853,"uid":77989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T17:33:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Respiratory system<br />\nDigestive system<br />\nReproductive system<br />\nLymphatic system <br />\nNervous system <br />\n呢啲基本啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實需唔需要好詳細咁熟讀哂每個system入面嘅部位？例如每一樣野既功能同特點？<br />\nthx絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去search medical surgical nursing e-book"},{"pid":"1d2251c0dc7347e87a935c6e222c9afa9b8889f5","tid":337853,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T18:23:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Respiratory system<br />\nDigestive system<br />\nReproductive system<br />\nLymphatic system <br />\nNervous system <br />\n呢啲基本啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實需唔需要好詳細咁熟讀哂每個system入面嘅部位？例如每一樣野既功能同特點？<br />\nthx絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要啦緊係"},{"pid":"c9121051041a68817eca9a5497ee25e7d6b61ccd","tid":337853,"uid":17530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T18:46:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Respiratory system<br />\nDigestive system<br />\nReproductive system<br />\nLymphatic system <br />\nNervous system <br />\n呢啲基本啦</blockquote><br />\n上YouTube 睇 <br />\n基本上都好詳細 溫哂佢 <br />\n大概就係教而啲 <br />\n利申：讀nursing"},{"pid":"ed60916e3f3029b416f45b33584e1a24021ac43c","tid":337853,"uid":131012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T03:51:58.000Z","msg":"除咗11 個system 此外，enzyme, DNA, RNA 嗰啲基本concept 學"},{"pid":"a33f3887b3770c01c9290086b657efa2789bda6e","tid":337853,"uid":131012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T03:53:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除咗11 個system 此外，enzyme, DNA, RNA 嗰啲基本concept <span style=\"color: red;\">都要</span>學</blockquote>"}]}